#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "There are two ways to change the current level. In both cases, you will "
#| "be considered as a cheater and you will not be able to register to the "
#| "high scores. The first way is using a cheatcode. I let you find it. The "
#| "other way is selecting the level you want from the "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Change Level</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog. See the <link linkend=\"menubar"
#| "\">Menubar</link> section for more details."
msgid ""
"There are two ways to change the current level. In both cases, you will be "
"considered as a cheater and you will not be able to register to the high "
"scores. The first way is using a cheatcode. I let you find it. The other way "
"is selecting the level you want from the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Change Level</guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog. See the "
"<link linkend=\"menu\">Menubar</link> section for more details."
msgstr ""
"Hai dúas formas de cambiar o nivel actual. Nos dous casos vaise considerar "
"que se fai trampa e non se poderá rexistrar unha puntuación alta. A primeira "
"forma é empregando unha lista de truques. Búscaa. A outra maneira é "
"escollendo o nivel desexado no nivel <menuchoice><guimenu>Partida</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Cambiar o nivel</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Consulta a "
"sección sobre a <link linkend=\"menubar\">barra do menú</link> para máis "
"detalles."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I change default keyboard shortcuts?"
msgstr "Pode cambiar os atallos predeterminados do teclado?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is not possible for now. But will be a new feature in a future version of "
"&kapman;. See the <link linkend=\"keybindings\">Default Keybindings</link> "
"section for more details."
msgstr ""
"Non é posíbel por agora. Pero será unha funcionalidade nova nunha versión "
"futura de &kapman;. Consulta a sección sbore <link linkend=\"keybindings"
"\">atallos predeterminados</link> para máis detalles."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Teño que saír do xogo, pero aínda non rematei a partida actual. Podo gardar "
"o progreso?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can not, and it is deliberate. We think that the game would be too easy "
"if you could save the game and reload it as you lose your lives."
msgstr ""
"Non podes, e é deliberado. Pensamos que o xogo sería demasiado doado se se "
"puidese gardar e cargar de novo segundo cando se perden as vidas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I get more lives?"
msgstr "Como podo obter máis vidas?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two ways to get lives. The first one is using a cheatcode. I let "
"you find it. The other way is winning points. Every 10,000 points, you get a "
"life more. See the <link linkend=\"rules\">Rules</link> section for more "
"details."
msgstr ""
"Hai dúas formas de obter vidas. A primeira é usando unha lista de truques. "
"Atópaa. A outra é gañando puntos. A cada 10.000 puntos obtense máis unha "
"vida. Consulta a sección <link linkend=\"rules\">Regras</link> para máis "
"detalles."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Configuration"
msgstr "Configuración do xogo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:262
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can select the theme you want to play &kapman;. To do that, select "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Kapman...</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice>. The &kapman; configuration dialog (see below) "
#| "appears and you can then select the theme. It is immediately changed on "
#| "validating your choice, no need to restart the game. You can click on the "
#| "<guibutton>Defaults</guibutton> button to restore the default theme."
msgid ""
"You can select the theme you want to play &kapman;. To do that, select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kapman;…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. The &kapman; configuration dialog (see below) "
"appears and you can then select the theme. It is immediately changed on "
"validating your choice, no need to restart the game. You can click on the "
"<guibutton>Defaults</guibutton> button to restore the default theme."
msgstr ""
"Pódese escoller o tema co que se quere xogar a &kapman;. Para facelo, "
"escolle <menuchoice><guimenu>Configuración</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configurar "
"Kapman..</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. O diálogo de configuración de &kapman; "
"(mira embaixo) aparece e nel pódese escoller o tema. Cámbiase inmediatamente "
"cando se valida esta escolla, non hai que reiniciar a partida. Pódese premer "
"o botón <guibutton>Predeterminado</guibutton> para restaurar o tema "
"predeterminado."

